00:36:00,358 --> 00:36:01,536
that someone
could have hurt her?

768
00:36:01,560 --> 00:36:03,776
There's a guy you
may want to look into.

769
00:36:03,811 --> 00:36:06,479
Um, he's an intern at Chastain.

770
00:36:06,514 --> 00:36:09,332
His name is Devon Pravesh.

771
00:36:11,703 --> 00:36:13,820
This is her work phone.

772
00:36:13,855 --> 00:36:15,155
We found it at her desk.

773
00:36:29,921 --> 00:36:32,906
Mm, I'm alive.

774
00:36:32,941 --> 00:36:35,091
And you're gonna stay that way.

775
00:36:35,126 --> 00:36:36,771
We had to place
a ventricular device

776
00:36:36,795 --> 00:36:39,012
to keep your heart
pumping effectively,

777
00:36:39,047 --> 00:36:41,581
and we'll schedule a transplant
eval when you're healed.

778
00:36:41,616 --> 00:36:44,351
Right now it's
working perfectly.

779
00:36:44,386 --> 00:36:45,746
And after PT

780
00:36:45,770 --> 00:36:48,666
and rehab, you'll be
able to walk again.

781
00:36:48,690 --> 00:36:51,374
Will I be able to go
back to the police force?

782
00:36:51,410 --> 00:36:53,826
We don't know that yet.

783
00:36:53,862 --> 00:36:56,229
But...

784
00:36:56,264 --> 00:36:58,581
you are gonna lose that cane.

785
00:36:58,617 --> 00:37:00,395
That much I can promise you.

786
00:37:00,419 --> 00:37:01,879
I hate that thing.

787
00:37:04,789 --> 00:37:06,790
You deserve to be happy.

788
00:37:09,761 --> 00:37:11,711
So do you.

789
00:37:11,746 --> 00:37:14,831
Your sister
would've wanted that.

790
00:37:18,086 --> 00:37:19,719
Thanks, guys.

791
00:37:39,090 --> 00:37:41,057
Easy on the hot water.

792
00:37:41,093 --> 00:37:42,742
Sit when you pee.

793
00:37:42,777 --> 00:37:45,628
You may use my condiments,
but do not touch my alcohol.

794
00:37:46,648 --> 00:37:48,298
I would never.

795
00:37:48,333 --> 00:37:50,311
Outside of the guest
room, it's either clothing

796
00:37:50,335 --> 00:37:52,285
or a bathrobe
with full coverage.

797
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:54,254
I don't want any surprises.

798
00:37:54,289 --> 00:37:56,289
Why are you helping me?

799
00:37:56,341 --> 00:37:58,925
Because you need it.

800
00:38:03,981 --> 00:38:05,681
Wayne Jackson.

801
00:38:05,717 --> 00:38:08,734
In asystole for 15 minutes
before anyone noticed.

802
00:38:08,770 --> 00:38:10,281
Kathy Mars. The hospital

803
00:38:10,305 --> 00:38:12,405
billed her 12 grand
for a damn bee sting.

804
00:38:12,441 --> 00:38:15,692
Matthew Teter came in
with stage IV colon cancer.

805
00:38:15,727 --> 00:38:17,839
He would've lived if
he'd had early detection.

806
00:38:17,863 --> 00:38:19,923
Every time I thought I got
close to making things better,

807
00:38:19,947 --> 00:38:24,100
I saw another patient
lose to a broken system.

808
00:38:24,135 --> 00:38:27,487
So, yes, it is about
the patients for me.

809
00:38:27,539 --> 00:38:31,290
But you're crazy if you
think you can change things.

810
00:38:31,343 --> 00:38:34,127
Maybe I am.

811
00:38:40,836 --> 00:38:43,636
I like crazy.

812
00:38:49,644 --> 00:38:52,145
- Yeah, sure.
- Here.

813
00:38:52,180 --> 00:38:54,714
We'll just, uh, get these...

814
00:38:54,749 --> 00:38:56,410
So the pay sucks.

815
00:38:56,434 --> 00:38:58,401
Beyond sucks.

816
00:38:58,436 --> 00:39:00,737
And Chastain could slash
our funding at any time?

817
00:39:00,772 --> 00:39:02,054
Without warning.

818
00:39:02,089 --> 00:39:04,424
I won't be bossed around.

819
00:39:05,893 --> 00:39:07,961
You start tomorrow.

820
00:39:07,996 --> 00:39:09,713
I start now.

821
00:39:12,384 --> 00:39:14,918
Congratulations.

822
00:39:14,953 --> 00:39:16,720
You graduated from the ICU.

823
00:39:16,755 --> 00:39:18,971
Eh. Yeah, unfortunately,

824
00:39:19,006 --> 00:39:20,723
not from clear liquids.

825
00:39:20,758 --> 00:39:22,926
You need something for the pain?

826
00:39:22,961 --> 00:39:23,927
No.

827
00:39:23,962 --> 00:39:26,579
No, I want to be alert for this.

828
00:39:26,615 --> 00:39:31,033
Son, I've been fighting
this disease for a while now.

829
00:39:31,068 --> 00:39:32,551
I got lucky this time,

830
00:39:32,604 --> 00:39:35,071
but it only gets
worse from here.

831
00:39:35,106 --> 00:39:38,324
Dr. Simmons says you will
be back on semisolid foods

832
00:39:38,359 --> 00:39:39,736
in a week. In two to three days,

833
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:40,871
you will be out of the hospital

834
00:39:40,895 --> 00:39:42,612
and starting physical therapy.

835
00:39:42,647 --> 00:39:45,376
- You will get
your strength back.
- We both know

836
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:48,601
my chances for a meaningful
recovery become less

837
00:39:48,637 --> 00:39:50,620
and less with each
surgery I have.

838
00:39:50,655 --> 00:39:52,956
I need you to stay positive.

839
00:39:52,991 --> 00:39:56,009
Patients who believe they'll
recover have better outcomes.

840
00:39:56,044 --> 00:39:58,261
Positive thinking won't
change what's happening

841
00:39:58,296 --> 00:40:00,446
to this body of mine.

842
00:40:00,481 --> 00:40:03,433
I'd like to formalize things.

843
00:40:09,558 --> 00:40:12,541
You want an advanced directive.

844
00:40:12,577 --> 00:40:14,394
If something like this

845
00:40:14,446 --> 00:40:16,445
happens to me again,

846
00:40:16,481 --> 00:40:19,598
I don't want my life prolonged

847
00:40:19,634 --> 00:40:21,879
by aggressive measures.

848
00:40:21,903 --> 00:40:23,453
That's a long way off.

849
00:40:23,488 --> 00:40:25,555
I'm serious.

850
00:40:25,590 --> 00:40:28,792
I need to know you'll
respect my wishes.

851
00:40:30,795 --> 00:40:33,179
Of course.

852
00:40:34,833 --> 00:40:37,467
Thank you.

853
00:40:39,337 --> 00:40:41,254
♪ ♪

854
00:41:01,943 --> 00:41:05,111
<i>Dear Board of Directors,</i>

855
00:41:05,146 --> 00:41:07,580
<i>Leading this hospital</i>

856
00:41:07,616 --> 00:41:09,765
<i>has been a joy and a privilege.</i>

857
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:11,934
<i>However, in the coming days,</i>

858
00:41:11,969 --> 00:41:15,171
<i>you will learn of a terrible
mistake I have made.</i>

859
00:41:15,206 --> 00:41:17,323
<i>I betrayed your trust.</i>

860
00:41:17,358 --> 00:41:19,437
<i>You deserve someone
who will always put</i>

861
00:41:19,461 --> 00:41:20,760
<i>this community first.</i>

862
00:41:20,795 --> 00:41:22,328
<i>And I am deeply ashamed</i>

863
00:41:22,363 --> 00:41:25,330
<i>that I have not always
been that person.</i>

864
00:41:25,383 --> 00:41:27,945
<i>I put my trust in
the wrong person.</i>

865
00:41:29,688 --> 00:41:32,388
Coming.

866
00:41:36,094 --> 00:41:39,529
<i>And I take full
responsibility for my actions.</i>

867
00:41:53,861 --> 00:41:57,730
<i>I will step down and step away.</i>

868
00:41:57,765 --> 00:42:00,349
<i>I hereby resign as CEO</i>

869
00:42:00,384 --> 00:42:02,752
<i>and Chief of Surgery.</i>

870
00:42:02,787 --> 00:42:05,938
<i>Dr. Randolph Bell.</i>

871
00:42:10,262 --> 00:42:12,478
Uh, Dr. Bell?

872
00:42:12,513 --> 00:42:13,846
You need to see this.

873
00:42:13,899 --> 00:42:15,348
Grayson, what?

874
00:42:15,383 --> 00:42:17,233
It's the news.

875
00:42:17,268 --> 00:42:20,403
<i>Shots fired in a Buckhead hotel.</i>

876
00:42:20,438 --> 00:42:21,916
<i>Police report they
found the body</i>

877
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:24,157
<i>of accused murderer
Dr. Lane Hunter.</i>

878
00:42:24,192 --> 00:42:26,120
<i>Recently out on bail
after several months</i>

879
00:42:26,144 --> 00:42:28,494
<i>in the Atlanta Detention Center,</i>

880
00:42:28,529 --> 00:42:30,257
<i>Hunter was arrested
for first-degree murder</i>

881
00:42:30,281 --> 00:42:32,431
<i>and involuntary manslaughter,</i>

882
00:42:32,467 --> 00:42:35,551
<i>as well as insurance fraud
and money laundering.</i>

883
00:42:35,587 --> 00:42:39,288
<i>No suspects have
been named in her death.</i>

884
00:42:39,323 --> 00:42:41,085
<i>In related news, victim
rights advocates...</i>

885
00:42:41,109 --> 00:42:43,459
Um... thank you, Grayson.

886
00:42:43,495 --> 00:42:44,743
You can go.

887
00:42:44,779 --> 00:42:45,761
<i>Not stepping forward,</i>

888
00:42:45,796 --> 00:42:47,546
<i>not commenting on the death.</i>

889
00:42:47,599 --> 00:42:51,050
<i>Many of them vocal just
months ago, and now they're not...</i>

